    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and quarter the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Bash the<strong> lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and remove the <strong>tough outer layer<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> of the lemongrass and set aside for later</p><p>Chop the <strong>softer inner core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
