          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with the<strong> chopped lemongrass</strong>, the<strong> remaining creamed coconut </strong>and the<strong> ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Add most of the <strong>coriander</strong>, including the stalks (save some whole leaves for garnish!) with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a splash of <strong>water</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>turmeric marinade</strong></p>",
