    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4] </span>pieces of <strong>baking paper </strong>(or tin foil) approx. the size of A3 sheets of paper and add the<strong> outer lemongrass layers</strong> with <strong>basa fillets</strong> to the middle of each piece of paper</p><p>Divide the <strong>turmeric marinade</strong> evenly over each basa fillet, top with a knob of <strong>butter alternative </strong>and scrunch the edges of the baking paper together to form a sealed parcel</p><p>Add the <strong>parcels</strong> to a baking tray</p>",
      "order": 5,
