    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 15 min or until the basa is cooked through – this is your <strong>turmeric basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>cucumber </strong>into discs on the diagonal and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes </strong>very<strong> </strong>finely</p>",
